# ==================================
# LINE Messaging API Configuration
# ==================================
# 
# LINE bot credentials are stored in the database (line_bot_config table).
# Configure them from the web UI: Management > ตั้งค่า LINE
#
# To set up LINE integration:
# 1. Create LINE Official Account at https://manager.line.biz/
# 2. Enable Messaging API in LINE Official Account Manager
# 3. Go to LINE Developers Console: https://developers.line.biz/console/
# 4. Get Channel ID, Channel Secret, and create Long-lived Access Token
# 5. Deploy Supabase Edge Functions:
#    - supabase functions deploy line-webhook
#    - supabase functions deploy line-push
# 6. Set Webhook URL in LINE Developers Console to:
#    https://your-project-id.supabase.co/functions/v1/line-webhook
# 7. Configure credentials from web UI and enable the bot
